channel.title: [PI] New shitty Project Insanity i edited || No 500/600+ gfx etc ||
channel.description:
Hello Mopar,
Well its been a while since i worked on a server and lost all my java knowledge; and i was adding a dungeoneering base and added it all, but somewhere along the lines i done something wrong (in the part of clickingbuttons.java) and i was to tired to fix it, so im just releasing this shit.
-fixed x-logging -fixed dupe -added minigames -fixed most minigame (more stable) -worked on duel arean -duel arena staking -added new home area -fixed npc clipping -found and fixed bugs in npc's -added new dds interval's -fixed godsword timers -Added Custom Quick Chat! (only 4-5 skills on it work but in v2 if i make 1 i will try and fix) -Added x10 hit Multiplier -Started adding dungeoneering base - need to add the clickingbuttons stuff(and fix w/e is wrong with that file) -started to add onto barrows - 1 door opens in the tunnel so far was adding puzzles etc. -has jrebel files and code in server, just download, install jrebel and change the paths(updates server edits without restart) basicly you can fix a dupe/glitch/bug etc and have it take effect on server by compiling and no restart.
-don't know if i added anything else from that; just check it out
now for some pics
EDIT:deleted first 2 images due to accidental advertisement, and i dont have them on computer anymore.
[IMG]http://i26.tinypic.com/2zgb1co.png[/img] [IMG]http://i25.tinypic.com/oggpe9.png[/img] [IMG]http://i28.tinypic.com/33mbbj4.png[/img] [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/5f3rsw.jpg[/img]
